description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which features an All In retreat that no one wants to go to, and a pizza party at Denise's house with BD Aaron. On The Real Housewives of New York, Jacques makes a triumphant return to do stand-up and lecture Ramona and Dorinda on bullying.


RHONY Recap: 23:35ish
